            bindings = <
         &kp Q  &kp W  &kp F                &kp P        &kp B        &kp J                 &kp L            &kp U                  &kp Y    &kp SINGLE_QUOTE
         &kp A  &kp R  &kp S                &mt LSHFT T  &kp G        &kp M                 &mt RSHFT N      &kp E                  &kp I    &kp O
&kp TAB  &kp Z  &kp X  &kp C                &kp D        &kp V        &kp K                 &kp H            &kp COMMA              &kp DOT  &kp FSLH          &kp SEMICOLON
                       &mt LEFT_ALT ESCAPE  &lt 1 SPACE  &kp LCTRL    &mt LEFT_SHIFT ENTER  &lt 2 BACKSPACE  &mt LEFT_ALT CAPSLOCK
