            bindings = <
           &kp EXCL       &kp AT        &kp HASH      &kp DOLLAR        &kp PERCENT          &kp CARET     &kp AMPERSAND  &kp STAR      &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS
           &kp NUMBER_1   &kp NUMBER_2  &kp NUMBER_3  &kp NUMBER_4      &kp NUMBER_5         &kp NUMBER_6  &kp NUMBER_7   &kp NUMBER_8  &kp NUMBER_9          &kp NUMBER_0
&kp GRAVE  &kp BACKSLASH  &trans        &trans        &kp LEFT_BRACKET  &kp RIGHT_BRACKET    &kp DOT       &kp MINUS      &kp EQUAL     &kp UNDERSCORE        &kp PLUS               &kp PERIOD
